   Contact Information
   How to Contact Congressman Gephardt

   Congressman Gephardt and his staff are available to address your needs.
   Please feel free to direct your questions, comments, and concerns to
   the following locations:

   St. Louis
   11140 South Towne Square, Room 201
   St. Louis, MO 63123
   (314) 894-3400

   Festus
   998 East Gannon Dr (first floor)
   Festus, MO
   (636) 937-6399
   Mailing address for this office: PO Box 392, Festus, MO 63028

   Please note that the Festus office is only open part-time. The hours
   are:
   Tuesday 1 p.m. - 5 p.m.
   Wednesday 9 a.m. - noon

   Washington, D.C.
   1236 Longworth House Office Building
   Washington, DC 20515
   (202) 225-2671

   Or, feel free to send Congressman Gephardt an email. Please be sure to
   include your U.S. postal address within the Third Congressional
   District if you would like to receive a written response.

